{"sn1.79:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.79 ","sn1.79:0.2":"8. Chetvavagga ","sn1.79:0.3":"Patheyyasutta ","sn1.79:1.1":"“Kimsu bandhati patheyyam, ","sn1.79:1.2":"kimsu bhoganamasayo; ","sn1.79:1.3":"Kimsu naram parikassati, ","sn1.79:1.4":"kimsu lokasmi dujjaham; ","sn1.79:1.5":"Kismim baddha puthu satta, ","sn1.79:1.6":"pasena sakuni yatha”ti. ","sn1.79:2.1":"“Saddha bandhati patheyyam, ","sn1.79:2.2":"siri bhoganamasayo; ","sn1.79:2.3":"Iccha naram parikassati, ","sn1.79:2.4":"iccha lokasmi dujjaha; ","sn1.79:2.5":"Icchabaddha puthu satta, ","sn1.79:2.6":"pasena sakuni yatha”ti. "}